        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JP for copy of his <hi rend="italic">Life on the earth</hi> [1860].</p>  
<p>Is sorry, but not surprised, to see that JP is "dead against" CD on the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
